The paper proposes a neural network algorithm for multi-label classification, which falls under the category of machine learning. Specifically, the algorithm uses cascade neural networks and adaptive first order gradient algorithm for training, which are commonly used in deep learning and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
